window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Sarah McGraw lives with her father and brother on the edge of town, beside a Staten Island garbage dump. When mutant rats escape from the dump and terrorize the town’s citizens, it’s up to Sarah and her younger brother, Michael, to stop them from taking over New York City.</p>"; 
